1
00:00:03,956 --> 00:00:06,793
According to the inner awakenment 
of the disciple

2
00:00:06,793 --> 00:00:08,523
is how they will see guru.

3
00:00:08,603 --> 00:00:11,863
[Guru | Instructions and Form]

4
00:00:12,063 --> 00:00:16,255
Guru Mahārāj deals with this 
in ‘Śrī Guru and His Grace’

5
00:00:16,485 --> 00:00:24,131
and cautioning us against 
being overly

6
00:00:24,131 --> 00:00:28,401
emphasizing 
the form of the guru.

7
00:00:28,401 --> 00:00:31,059
Like we hear: 
vāṇī and vapu.

8
00:00:31,079 --> 00:00:35,289
Vāṇī—instructions, 
vapu—the form.

9
00:00:35,289 --> 00:00:37,655
And Guru Mahārāj says, 
even as a side point,

10
00:00:37,655 --> 00:00:40,342
even vani can turn into 
a type of vapu,

11
00:00:40,342 --> 00:00:45,500
if it becomes lifeless, mindless
parroting of instructions.

12
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:50,951
But that said, we see, there is picture:
the guru when he’s a young man,

13
00:00:50,951 --> 00:00:53,271
the guru in middle age, 
the guru in old age—

14
00:00:53,271 --> 00:00:54,472
which form is it?

15
00:00:54,472 --> 00:00:57,683
That form before us 
of Bhakti Vinod Ṭhākur,

16
00:00:57,683 --> 00:00:58,763
the beard …

17
00:00:58,763 --> 00:01:01,358
and I’ve told as once 
on his veranda in Calcutta

18
00:01:01,358 --> 00:01:03,878
Gurudev said, 
“And to think,

19
00:01:03,878 --> 00:01:08,228
he is a fourteen-year-old girl 
in Vṛndāvan!”

20
00:01:08,228 --> 00:01:11,761
So, how will you recognize 
Bhakti Vinod Ṭhākur?

21
00:01:11,761 --> 00:01:15,346
How will you recognize 
Guru Mahārāj, Gurudev,

22
00:01:15,346 --> 00:01:18,832
Saraswatī Ṭhākur, 
Śrīla Swāmī Mahārāj?

23
00:01:18,832 --> 00:01:22,602
Not by the picture
that you saw here.

24
00:01:22,602 --> 00:01:27,054
Does it mean 
to deprecate the picture?

25
00:01:27,054 --> 00:01:30,414
But that is we worship the picture—
the form of the Guru.

26
00:01:30,414 --> 00:01:37,274
But in that plane they’ll be recognized 
by devotional tendency.

